    "attributes": {
        "action": "Give retained firefighters the right to have lights/sirens on personal vehicle",
        "additional_details": "The reason I think the UK Government should give retained firefighter the right to have any colour flashing light on there personal vehicle is because no one knows when a retained firefighter is responding to a call that could be life threatening. Every minute counts.",
        "background": "Give all retained firefighters the right to have any colour lights and sirens on personal vehicle so people know when there are responding to the station for call. Don\u2019t have to give them the right to speed.",
